author: KJ
text: Today I understand that when someone goes overboard with criticism, either with themselves or another person, its bcoz they're just being human too - we're all still in the process of learning (a lot!) from life 💟🥰

author: KJ
text: I am still struggling with self criticism, but starting to learn that even "doing my best" can result in failure and dissatisfaction, coz we are humans, its normal and we even dont realize that not bcoz the outcome wasnt exaactly as expected, it has to be bad.

author: KJ
text: Dont b so concerned bout what others think bout u, sometimes they just cant do better, its no ones fault, take it easy on u. Anxiety bout situations out of ur control/not the way u imagined ("bad") doesnt help, learn to thank 4 the shitty moments in life, they bring good stuff 2 https://t.co/EUdsWAot0P
